78db428748c","tid":1722162,"uid":121324,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"2dfb61a5078973d98032b92935832c3f181384e7","tid":1722162,"uid":280612,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T23:23:15.000Z","msg":"由而家開始，將凌晨三點個記招正名為鄭乘隆deal"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:22:31.000Z","msg":"諗諗點解尋晚無再強攻中大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為要派鬼入去<br />\n整場運動無大台<br />\n而家幫你大台化<br />\n做個膠決定，令你中大人不代表我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用公路換區選，同你講咁做係將個波交比政府一定係吹風狗<br />\n即係話，一日未到區選，無論對方做乜野，呢段時間你自己鎖死自己唔可以再用公路戰法<br />\n<br />\n若果對方無反口，<br />\n參考多份報章頭版都係叫人投票，<br />\n可能係佢本身都有照常區選呢個打算，<br />\n白賺你永久自廢武功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而若果最後對方反口，<br />\n對方無損失之餘，<br />\n都只會係你自己平白棄權咗一個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而呢一個星期，<br />\n可以比狗回氣，<br />\n可以因為斷咗連續性罷工條氣，發生一星期內止暴製亂，到時候你無得再講條件<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mCekY6w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmCekY6w.png&h=6ef838e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n怕你唔肯接受政府條件袋住先<br />\n幫你自己割地讓步"},{"pid":"68ceb344f76e6911dd619929ae8bf933c0747661","tid":1722162,"uid":141033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:24:41.000Z","msg":"當時又冇強力反對？發酵咗成晚柒咗先有聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a40c68892cf9528eb7fe9f466db0b6b5ea2ef7","tid":1722162,"uid":228205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"個標題驚開得唔好，開多個<br />\n<br />\n有鬼騎劫中大，唔係唔屌得下話？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722384</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"feb6